author: Coingape Staff
title: Dogwifhat Smart Whale Dumps Heavily Booking Profit, Has WIF Price Topped?
text: Highlights - Dogwifhat smart whale sparks market discussions with massive dump. - The whale swaps WIF for SOL, in turn booking profits. - WIF price crashed intraday, with investors speculating on future movements. A Dogwifhat smart whale caused a stir across the broader cryptocurrency landscape on Friday, heavily dumping the dog-themed meme token. Recent on-chain statistics indicate that the smart whale traded a whopping 850K coins to book a notable profit of $7.5 million. This trade strategy garnered significant attention as WIF price crashed over 15% intraday, sparking uncertain investor sentiments over whether the token may have topped amid a bull market. Dogwifhat Smart Whale Dumps 850K Tokens Sparking Market Speculations According to the data offered by Lookonchain on November 15, a smart whale was recorded dumping 850,000 Dogwifhat tokens, in turn swapping it for 15,987 SOL worth $3.4 million. As per the data, the smart whale address 3cBB2Z.. made the trades. However, despite the massive dump, the whale still held 50,000 WIF, worth $175K. Notably, the whale booked a total profit of $7.5 million on the [leading dog-themed meme token](https://coingape.com/top-dog-themed-memecoins/) with the mentioned trades weighing in. While this profit-making strategy underscored the meme coin’s potential to offer substantial gains, it also signaled a loss of investor confidence in the asset’s future potential. Besides, the massive dump sparks bearish concerns among traders amid a bull market while the existing holding still projects some optimism on price ahead, sparking market speculations. Also, on-chain data showed that the whale also booked a notable profit on recently listed the Solana meme coin PNUT. The whale spent 3,800 SOL to bag 1.74 million PNUT, now holding an unrealized profit of $2.07 million. [Solscan’s data](https://solscan.io/account/3cBB2ZyoNy8YEquSSzR2Rpggp9vcrfz4NcbCKHp7BzvT) showed that other token holdings by the same address included GIGACHAD (GIGA) and Chaos and Disorder (CHAOS), among other tokens. Overall, market participants speculate over WIF price action’s future in light of the massive dump and an intraday crash. What’s Next For WIF Price? At press time, WIF price crashed 16% over the past day and is now trading at $3.54. The coin’s 24-hour low and high were $3.38 and $4.33, respectively. Further, the token’s intraday trading volume dipped 48% to $1.99 billion today. This slumping action aligns with the declining market confidence for the asset, as illustrated by the abovementioned massive dump. Meanwhile, Coinglass data indicated that the Dogwifhat futures OI dipped 19% to $609.02 million today. Moreover, the derivatives volume also plunged 41% to $4.17 billion. This data further signaled a loss of investor interest in the asset. Nevertheless, in light of a bullish crypto market in Q4 as an aftermath of Donald Trump’s win in the U.S. elections, the crypto market glimmers hope for future movements. In the wake of these bullish aspects, a recent [Dogwifhat price analysis](https://coingape.com/markets/will-dogwifhat-price-hit-ath-this-week/) by CoinGape Media indicated that the token also eyes a new ATH shortly ahead. Although this bullish projection comes contrary to the selloff, market watchers continue to extensively monitor the token as sentiments of further gains prevail. title: 'Big Boost To Foreign Investors Like Us': Singapore Hails ULFA's Peace Accord With Centre, Assam Govt
text: - By ANI - Published: Sat, 30 Dec 2023 09:31 PM (IST) - Source:ANI Singapore has lauded India's historic signing of a peace accord with the United Liberation Front of Assam (ULFA), saying that it will significantly enhance foreign investments from Singapore in the Northeast region. Singapore High Commissioner to India, Simon Wong took to social media platform X (formerly Twitter) to express his appreciation for the tripartite peace pact between ULFA, the Centre and the Assam government. "We are happy to see the historic tripartite peace pact signed amongst ULFA, GOI and the Govt of Assam. This will anchor peace in the region and give a big boost to foreign investors like Singapore to move into the Northeast," Wong posted on X. We are happy to see the historic tripartite peace pact signed amongst ULFA, GOI and the Govt of Assam. This will anchor peace in the region and give a big boost to foreign investors like Singapore to move into the Northeast. - HC Wong— Singapore in India (@SGinIndia) [@PMOIndia] [@CMOfficeAssam] [@HMOIndia] [https://t.co/u0QuyPRXvH] [December 30, 2023] Earlier on Friday, United Liberation Front of Assam (ULFA)'s pro-talks faction signed a tripartite Memorandum of Settlement pact with the Centre and the Assam government on Friday in the presence of Union Home Minister Amit Shah. The Singapore envoy made the comments while reacting to the post of Assam Chief Minister Himanta Biswa Sarma, who had called it a "historic day" and said that this step is in the direction of lasting peace and progress in Assam. "Guided by the sterling vision and blessings of Hon'ble PM Shri @narendramodi ji efforts for lasting peace and progress in Assam received a historic impetus today. The Memorandum of Settlement, signed under the guidance of Hon'ble HM Shri @AmitShah ji, stands out for many reasons," CM Sarma stated. He said that the agreement draws the curtains on Assam's "oldest armed resistance pursued by ULFA, protects the interests of our people and paves way for spurring growth in the region". Calling it a special day for 'Bharat', Sarma further added that those who were once associated with violence will become partners in the nation's progress. "For an entire generation, the insurgency had stymied the potential of Assam. The single-minded pursuit of inclusive development by Hon'ble PM since 2014 has resulted in today's transformative achievement which marks a new dawn of harmony and togetherness," he stated. A 29-member delegation of the ULFA's pro-talks delegation, including 16 ULFA members and 13 from civil society, signed the agreement on Friday. This a significant pact as the banned ULFA-Independent has been the only major insurgent outfit in the state after the ULFA pro-talks faction signed the agreement with the Centre and Assam government. The separatist ULFA was formed in April 1979 in the aftermath of an agitation against undocumented immigrants from Bangladesh (erstwhile East Pakistan). It split into two groups in February 2011 with the Arabinda Rajkhowa-led faction giving up violence and agreeing to unconditional talks with the government. Paresh Baruah, who leads the other rebranded ULFA-Independent faction, is against the talks. The pro-talks faction has sought constitutional and political reforms for the protection of the identity and resources of Assam's indigenous people including their right to land. The Union government in April sent it a draft agreement. An earlier round of talks between the two sides was held in Delhi in August. Notably, the BJP-led Centre has signed peace deals with rebel Bodo, Dimasa, Karbi, and Adivasi outfits in Assam over the last three years. Meanwhile, Union Home Minister Amit Shah has assured the United Liberation Front of Assam (ULFA) pro-talks faction of time-bound implementation of the agreement that was signed. author: VNExplorer
title: À Paris, un gros orage provoque des éclairs et pluies diluviennes ce jeudi soir
text: Les éclairs près de la tour Eiffel le 1er août 2024. MÉTÉO - Le ciel zébré d’éclairs et des rues transformées en ruisseaux. Un gros orage a touché Paris et la région Île-de-France, ce jeudi 1er août au soir, en plein Jeux olympiques. Les images postées sur les réseaux sociaux sont impressionnantes. Après des orages diluviens dans les Vosges, les images de la « crue éclair » et des coulées de boue L’orage a débuté en milieu de soirée, d’abord avec des éclairs. La pluie abondante est arrivée quelques minutes plus tard, comme vous pouvez le voir dans les images ci-dessous. Comme l’a souligné la journaliste Alexandra Blanc, le match de basket 3x3 France-Serbie à la Concorde a d’ailleurs dû être interrompu pendant 30 minutes. Défaite des Bleus à la reprise. Le Parisien ajoute le match suivant a été reprogrammé et qu’un match de beach-volley a aussi été arrêté quelques minutes. Crues dans les Vosges Météo France avait placé une dizaine de départements en vigilance orange à la canicule ce jeudi soir, mais cette alerte concernait principalement le sud-ouest de l’Hexagone. Elle ne faisait pas état de fortes pluies attendues en Île-de-France, à part dans la Seine-et-Marne placée en vigilance orange crues. Les autres départements étaient en alerte jaune. Ils sont repassés en vert à minuit. La capitale n’a pas été la seule touchée. Le département des Vosges, placé en vigilance jaune aux orages par Météo France, était également victime d’une crue éclair après le passage du tonnerre et des averses dans l’après-midi. Dans la nuit de mercredi à jeudi déjà, les intempéries intenses avaient surpris les Parisiens qui ont assisté à des éclairs en série. Gros orages également à Évreux en Normandie, où près de trois semaines de pluies sont tombées en une heure, dans l’Eure, ou encore dans la région lyonnaise. title: #21 Fe, familia y odio al progresismo: el poder de los evangélicos latinos se extiende por Estados Unidos
text:
blodhemna elpais.com #4 Es una manera de verlo. Otra es que unos cuantos españoles se han marchado a países menos corruptos, han visto que se vive mejor así y evitan votar a los partidos que mantienen aquí niveles indecentes de corrupción.
Pero hay de todo…
#4 te recomiendo algo más de fibra en tu dieta, parece que aún no has digerido el que no ganaran los tuyos
#4 que yo conozca la gente que emigra a EEUU normalmente son gente con títulos superiores donde irse a América es muy buena opción laboral, y ya esta, si votan a la izquierda española sera porque ven desde fuera que es mejor opción.
Que pasa con los que votan a la derecha?
Que significaria?
Por cierto a mayor nivel de estudios el votante de izquierda aumenta, tampoco dices nada de eso?
Y los testigos de Jehová. Antes estaban a la salida de los hospitales con sus plafones. Ahora los veo en: la salida del metro, de los parques y en cualquier esquina o paseo. De 3 en 3. Si no les miras no te molestan, al menos en mi experiencia, pero me parece preocupante cómo van invadiendo el espacio público para su negocio de proselitismo religioso. ¿Puedo plantar un plafón con folletos de mi empresa 7 u 8 horas allá dónde me apetezca y abordar a los transeúntes?
#3 al igual que llevan toda la vida ocupando espacio publico los mendigos, los que reparten folletos, los grupos de turistas guiados.... mientras la ocupacion no sea permanente, no hay problema
#3 En mi pequeña ciudad de 40k habitantes el otro día me crucé a cuatro así, todos eran latinos. Les dije con palabras poco amables que se fueran con sus historias a su templo, que la calle no era lugar para ello. Eran muy ridículos, hablaban con una grandiosidad típica de pastor evangélico y que si la gloria de dios y mierdas así. Llamé a la policía. Me parece sumamente preocupante esto. Uno de ellos aún venía con ese falso buen rollo a "debatir" conmigo y me hacía preguntas de lo más ridículas. Largo de la calle por favor.
Yo lo llamaría "fe seudocristiana", porque muchas veces esto no está movido por una fe religiosa, sino que la fe religiosa es solo el medio para mover otra cosa, por ejemplo, mantener a la gente distraída odiando el aborto o a los homosexuales mientras no se dan cuenta de que otros se están quedando con la mayor parte de su esfuerzo al trabajar.
La religión era prácticamente la única cosa de LATAM que EEUU no controlaba, pero con el evangelismo es probable que en una década o dos reemplace al catolicismo en cantidad de seguidores.
